LLM vs RAG

| LLM Only                          | LLM + RAG                           |
| --------------------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| Uses training knowledge           | Uses your latest documents          |
| Can hallucinate                   | More accurate                       |
| Doesn't know private company data | Knows your uploaded PDFs            |
| Knowledge may be outdated         | Can use updated files               |
| Good for general questions        | Best for company-specific questions |


The Complete Flow
               User Question
                     │
                     ▼
      "What is the warranty period?"
                     │
                     ▼
       Convert Question to Embedding
                     │
                     ▼
          Search FAISS / ChromaDB
                     │
                     ▼
      Retrieve Top Relevant Chunks
                     │
                     ▼
