Why Doesn't OpenAI Store Every Company's Data?

Suppose there are:

100 million companies
10 billion PDFs
New documents every day

It is impossible to retrain the LLM every time a document changes.

Instead:

Company PDF

↓

Vector Database

↓

RAG

↓

LLM

No retraining is needed.

